video_title: Unlock the Secret to Knowing Who Is Truly in Your Corner!
transcript:
so how do you know if you're surrounding
yourself with the right people it's
super simple you take a look at the five
people that you spend the most time with
and you ask yourself a simple question
if I have children would I want my
children to grow up to be exactly like
that person if the answer is yes you're
surrounding yourself with the right
people if the answer is no you need to
start making some new friends
